name: January What's In-die Box
description:
Preorder for the January 2014 What's In-die Box

January's Theme is "The Muppets"

5 Exclusive Australian Indie Polishes from:

Lilypad Lacquer
Peita's Polish
Glam Polish
Alanna Renee
Glittering Elements


Orders open until 28th December 2013, boxes will ship 2nd week of January.


The polishes made for What's In-die Box will not be available for sale after January, they are exclusive to the box!!

International postage price is for registered airmail, this is why it is a little more. As these are Limited Edition polishes I prefer to have the parcels registered. I am happy to ship to an Australian friend's address.
